  "snapshot": "os",
  "instruction": "A local project brief is already available in Chrome at file:///home/user/Desktop/ui_brand_refresh_brief.html. Use VS Code to update /home/user/Desktop/ui_brand_refresh from the provided starter into a stronger launch page. Preserve header.site-header, section#hero, and footer.site-footer. Add section#testimonials after the feature grid with exactly 2 article.quote-card blocks that use the local avatar images assets/avatar-ops.svg and assets/avatar-design.svg. Add a sticky demo callout as aside#request-demo.sticky-demo with a button labeled Request Demo. Update manifest.json so project is ui-brand-refresh, theme is ember, version is 2.1, and previewPort is 8123. Start a local preview server for the project and finish with Chrome open at http://127.0.0.1:8123/index.html. Keep all assets local; do not leave remote image URLs in the final bundle.",
